{"type": "article", "id": 23813, "title": "纯白色的化妆品包装", "description": "", "date": "2016-03-14T07:00:25Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 34, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607105821KTWQrmtNBpI81nw3.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这是瑞士化妆品牌 Nahua Cosmetics 的包装系列，从纸袋、盒子到装化妆品的容器本身一律采用白色，显得很纯净，传达出少用添加剂的意思。花纹和 logo 都用很细的银色线条，通过反光来表现深浅，整体显示出干净和优雅。花纹的灵感源于阿兹特克人（Aztec）的装饰，他们是在墨西哥的印第安人，生产的 chia oil（奇雅子油）被称为快乐精油，可以加工成美容产品或营养保健品。设计师来自波兰，<a href=\"http://www.dominikpacholczyk.com/work/nahua-cosmetics/\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607105819DZwFPoauHEx3Qcep.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607105819VNH5EBi6XyTo7LOK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56203704\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607105820WOJagVsB3Sxb8hKq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56203704\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071058205txBMOXPosNJqhE1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607105821IqRhLKsNH6FE0o5P.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56203704\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}